Our Main Products

 Through professional and one-stop shop service, Yieh Corp. integrates entire resources of steel businesses of E Untied Group and related affiliates, offering stainless steel, carbon steel and carbon steel, alloy steel, aluminum and other metal products. 




Stainless Steel


Hot Rolled Coil, Cold Rolled Coil, Strip, Plate, Stainless Steel Checker Plate, Stainless Steel Sheet ...




Carbon Steel


Carbon Steel Hot Rolled Coil / Strip / Plate / Sheet, Carbon Steel Cold Rolled Coil / Strip / Sheet ...




Coated Steel


Galvanized Steel, Galvalume, Galvafan, PPGI, PPGL, PPGF, EGI ...




Pipe / Tube


Welded and Seamless Pipes / Tubes, Alloy Steel Seamless Pipes / Tubes, High Steel Grade Line Pipes ...




Aluminum


Aluminum Coil / Strip/ Sheet / Plate/ Foil, Embossed Aluminum Coil / Plate, Coated Aluminum Coil / Sheet ...




Bar


Stainless Steel Bar, Carbon Steel Bar, Hot Rolled Reinforcing Bar, Special Steel Bar ...




Wire Rod


Stainless Steel Wire Rod, Stainless Steel Wire, Carbon Steel Wire Rod, Carbon Steel Wire ...




Others


Cutting Fluid, Silicon Steel, Titanium / Nickel & Alloy, Wear-resistant High Manganese Alloy Steel Mn13, ...









