Company Description                    




                        Yieh United Steel Corporation (YUSCO) was founded in December 1988. The plant is located in Kaohsiung County, southern Taiwan. YUSCO is the largest integrated stainless steel mill in Southeast Asia. YUSCO has a strong workforce and adopted state-of-the-art technology and equipment.  Each process and product is monitored by a computerized system for strict quality control.  Certified by ISO 9002 AND 14001, YUSCO is committed to meet its customers’ requirements. YUSCO produces high-quality and a diversified product mix to downstream processors.                    


